If we consider match-stmt, matchExpr cannot be null.
In every match-pattern, we try keep the matchExpr of match-stmt. If we consider list-match-pattern, we cannot say the matchExpr of list-match-pattern must be same as the matchExpr of member-match-patterns. Consider below example.
match v {
    [1, 2] => {} 
}

matchExpr of [1,2] (list-match-apttern) is v. But ew cannot apply the same thing to member-match-patterns which means 1 and 2.

